Achievements.Name: Precise 40/20
Achievements.Description: Kick a 40/20.

Achievements.Name: Put Some Touch On It
Achievements.Description: Drag the ball carrier over the sideline.

Achievements.Name: Pathfinder
Achievements.Description: Score a try by diving on a loose ball.

Achievements.Name: Controlled
Achievements.Description: Complete a tackle while using controlled movement.

Achievements.Name: Showboat
Achievements.Description: Taunt and then score a try with the same player.

Achievements.Name: In the Corner
Achievements.Description: Score a diving try in the corner and hit the corner post.

Achievements.Name: Drive it home
Achievements.Description: Drive the defence back over try line to score a try.

Achievements.Name: High Flyer
Achievements.Description: Score a try from a contested collect.

Achievements.Name: Niners
Achievements.Description: Win a match using Auckland Nines ruleset as the home team.

Achievements.Name: Sharing Is Caring
Achievements.Description: Upload a created player in The Fanhub.

Achievements.Name: Club Debut
Achievements.Description: Complete your first career match as a rookie player (any difficulty).

Achievements.Name: Sneak Attack
Achievements.Description: Score a try with dummy half after a scoot.

Achievements.Name: Golden Child
Achievements.Description: Win a match in golden point.

Achievements.Name: Disciplined
Achievements.Description: Complete a match without giving away a penalty.

Achievements.Name: Best Form Of Defence
Achievements.Description: Drag the ball carrier back into their own in goal.

Achievements.Name: Denier
Achievements.Description: Perform a successful charge down to prevent a field goal in extra time.

Achievements.Name: Catch Me If You Can
Achievements.Description: Run over 80m to score a try without being tackled - veteran difficulty or above.

Achievements.Name: Comeback Kids
Achievements.Description: Win a match when behind by 18+ points - veteran difficulty or above.

Achievements.Name: Brick Wall
Achievements.Description: Keep your opposition scoreless in a match and win on legend difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Nail Biter
Achievements.Description: Score to win a match in the final minute (in-game time).

Achievements.Name: Chippy
Achievements.Description: Score a try from a chip 'n' chase.

Achievements.Name: Hat Trick Hero
Achievements.Description: Score 3 tries with a single player in a match - veteran difficulty or above.

Achievements.Name: MVP
Achievements.Description: Be man of the match 5 times as a career player in a single season.

Achievements.Name: Best Of The Best
Achievements.Description: Win the Dally M or Man of Steel award in an NRL or Super League season in career mode.

Achievements.Name: Better Than The Rest
Achievements.Description: Win a premiership or championship in career mode

Achievements.Name: Captain Courageous
Achievements.Description: Get your career rookie to be promoted to team captain.

Achievements.Name: State Of Origin
Achievements.Description: Represent your state in career mode after beginning your career as a rookie.

Achievements.Name: Around The Grounds
Achievements.Description: Play a match at every licensed stadium.

Achievements.Name: Represent
Achievements.Description: Represent your country in career mode after beginning your career as a rookie.

Achievements.Name: Unbeatable
Achievements.Description: With 1 team go through an NRL/Super League season in career without conceding a loss.

Achievements.Name: Team Of The Year
Achievements.Description: Have six or more players from your team represent team of the year (coach mode).
